.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"fcccddd5e939a2919a4b76a6e076d5356f2ab77a","tid":1391694,"uid":291895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:57:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8576dfd593a59e6ea74add92f3ccf7a7351412c8","tid":1391694,"uid":283504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"【青少年醫肚行動】<br />\n<br />\nA.申請資格：<br />\n<br />\n1.經濟有困難、營養不足、餐餐「營多」m記的青年人<br />\n<br />\n2.年齡：12至35歲<br />\n<br />\nB.申請方法：<br />\n<br />\ntg @yannie25 /65469077 黎小姐或 tg @wongsiu /56217197 王小姐申請，而登記不用實名，提供化名也可。<br />\n<br />\nC.支援方式：<br />\n<br />\n1.快餐店券/超市券/小店飯票(各區有飯票小店 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2LPJxia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LPJxia&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=9af20f4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2LPJxia</a>)/已增值的八達通<br />\n<br />\n2.資助範圍：用膳、食物<br />\n<br />\n3.所有資料絕對保密，並會與申請者共商食物券交收。<br />\n<br />\n4.不限於北區，適用於全港性<br />\n<br />\n5.不限申請次數，用得合宜即可。<br />\n<br />\nD.請支持「青少年醫肚行動」：<br />\n<br />\n1.為了保障所有支持者安全及私隱，請盡可能購買超市/飯票/已增值的八達通。(為何盡可能不收取金錢？因考慮現時政治及輿論緊張的狀況。如你無法購買超市券只能予現金，請把現金自行拿到教會奉獻箱，或個別安排。這是為了保障你的安全，請勿為此行動用銀行過數)，同樣的請tg @yannie25 /65469077 黎小姐或 tg @wongsiu /56217197 王小姐處理你的支持行動。<br />\n<br />\n2.請到快餐店買券(最普及是大X樂現金券。我地唔收m記，真冇咩營養) /超市券/小店飯票(請參各區有飯票小店：  <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2LPJxia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LPJxia&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=9af20f4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2LPJxia</a>)<br />\n<br />\n3..我們會與你相約交收食物券，嘗試派人到各區收集。如真的太遠，請郵寄到：上水新康街12號2/f (請勿寫回郵地址，也留意不可郵寄現金，屬違法的。但八達通可寄。另外，可親身放到教會信箱)。<br />\n<br />\n*如果你想為青少年提供食物以外更多的援助，請inbox我們、wts app陳傳道，或tg @roywwjd ，作進一步了解。<br />\n<br />\n**「守護孩子行動」也需要現金支持，銀髮族總將好的留給下一代呢！<br />\n<br />\n***再提，請勿為行動而用銀行過數。但你若堅持希望付現金，請投到教會(上水新康街12號2/f，即3樓)奉獻箱，或到教會攀談一下！<br />\n<br />\n行動查詢：56217197 王小姐/65469077 黎小姐/60770032 陳凱興傳道<br />\n<br />\n「愛裡沒有懼怕，愛既完全，就把懼怕除去」約翰一書 4：18<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvuDzVH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvuDzVH.png&h=995d113f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ecbb4bb4791556d1b5745c88fbc58886b63f1a9","tid":1391694,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc3aefa2c1586642910c511ddbd60133e5b77f5","tid":1391694,"uid":283504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/31/220613_5c8fb9c574dc155f53937e511701e940.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F31%2F220613_5c8fb9c574dc155f53937e511701e940.png&h=0d4936c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d4d070f3a47d85aca49395aaefe161ca4715d27","tid":1391694,"uid":283504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:15:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c934d4044a4ea58df25d6ecd569c0c4d8e6f6027","tid":1391694,"uid":290027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8e30a1fbebe0eeb9c69d38509e280e61c812458","tid":1391694,"uid":283504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d725c99507702809a078e71f8968a95df0a1f48","tid":1391694,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abDpOOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abDpOOU</a><br />\n<br />\nTG grou